titles.title: A bill to extend the temporary suspension of duty on fluazifop-p-butyl.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 3/16/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend, through December 31, 1996, the existing suspension of duty on butyl 2-(4-(5-trifluoromethyl-2-pyridinyloxy)phenoxy)propanoate) (also known as fluazifop-p-butyl).
